Filesystem — Scoped file access

Operational Guides
Getting Started
Run: npm i -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code

Navigate: cd your-project && claude

Create CLAUDE.md with your project conventions

Add slash commands in .claude/commands/

Configure MCP in .mcp.json

Add skills as your workflows grow

Context Management
0-50% context — Work normally

50-70% context — Monitor usage

70-80% context — Run /compact

80%+ context — /clear mandatory

